/03/12/national/science-health/last-resort-coronavirus-treatment-japan-hospitals/ 'Last resort' COVID-19 treatment in short supply at Japan's hospitals]. [[Japan Times]]. March 12, 2020.</ref>\n|-\n| {{Flagicon|CHN}}[[Mainland China]] || Asia || || approx. 400 (in 2020)<ref>[https://finance.sina.cn/2020-02-10/detail-iimxyqvz1806334.d.html \u75ab\u60c5\u5173\u952e\u65f6\u523b\u6551\u547d\u7684ECMO:\u5168\u56fd\u53ea\u6709400\u53f0 \u4e3a\u4f55\u8fd9\u4e48\u5c11\uff1f] {{LL|zh}}. [[Sina Corp]]. February 10, 2020</ref>\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|2|refs=\n<ref name=\"pmid21825216\">{{cite journal |doi=10.1001/archneurol.2011.209 |pmid=21825216 |title=Neurological Injury in Adults Treated With Extracorporeal Membrane Oxygenation |volume=68 |issue=12 |journal=Archives of Neurology |pages=1543\u20139|year=2011 |last1=Mateen |first1=Farrah J. |last2=Muralidharan |first2=R. |last3=Shinohara |first3=R. T. |last4=Parisi |first4=J. E. |last5=Schears |first5=G. J. |last6=Wijdicks |first6=E. F. |doi-access=free }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"pmid15818357\">{{cite journal |doi=10.1053/j.pcsu.2005.02.004 |title=Decision making for mechanical cardiac assist in pediatric cardiac surgery |year=2005 |last1=Cohen |first1=Gordon |last2=Permut |first2=Lester |journal=Seminars in Thoracic and Cardiovascular Surgery: Pediatric Cardiac Surgery Annual |volume=8 |pages=41\u201350 |pmid=15818357}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RadiologySource\">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/j.jpeds.2004.07.010 |title=Post-conceptional age and IVH in ECMO patients |year=2004 |last1=Jobe |first1=Alan H. |journal=The Journal of Pediatrics |volume=145 |issue=2 |pages=A2}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"pmid19028644\">{{cite journal |pmid=19028644 |year=2008 |last1=Vural |first1=Kerem M. |title=Ventricular assist device applications |volume=8 |issue=Suppl 2 |pages=117\u2013130 |journal=Anadolu Kardiyoloji Dergisi |url=http://www.anatoljcardiol.com/jvi.aspx?un=AJC-93546}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"pmid9310799\">{{cite journal |doi=10.1007/s0